  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the <span class=\"italic \">xy</span>-plane, the graph of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals, x squared minus 9 \"></span></span> intersects line&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">p</span> at <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the point with coordinates 1 comma a\"></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the point with coordinates 5 comma b\"></span></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">a</span> and <span class=\"italic\">b</span> are constants. What is the slope of line&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">p </span>?</p>\n",
